<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Sterling" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Sterling,</orth> adj. of full value: <cit><quote>if my word be s. yet in England,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 4.264" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 264</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>with s. money,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.1.131" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 1, 131</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>you have ta'en these tenders for true pay, which are not s.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 1.3.107" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 3, 107</bibl></cit>.
